title: Shower head cover

claims.preamble: I claim the ornamental design for a shower head cover, as shown and described.

description: The claimed shower head cover may be placed over an existing shower head in an existing shower enclosure, or a variety of shower heads may be used, and installed inside the shower cover upon installation in a newly constructed shower stall.
